name: src/concepts/target.js
TargetSelector
description: The target selector
examples:
const target = new TargetSelector('p');
target.toString(); // @p

const targetWithArgs = new TargetSelector('p', {
  coordinate: [x, y, z],
  radius: [min, max],
  gamemode: Gamemode.ALL,
  count: 3,
  level: [min, max],
  score: [min, max],
  team: 'Red',
  name: 'name',
  volume: [dx, dy, dz],
  vertical: [min, max],
  horizontal: [min, max],
  type: 'Creeper'
});
